snippet.title: The Last Meadow (Discord April Fools Game) - Full Playthrough w/ All Achievements Unlocked
snippet.description:
Discord opened their own video game studio, Big Wump Games, for April Fools Day, and released their debut title, "The Last Meadow". This game will be available in the Discord client from now until April 7th. And what is it? Well, it is a clicker game where you simply... touch grass. Yes, the entire game is just a clicker game where you touch grass until you finally are able to go back home to your computer, and this game is very similar to other clicker games from the genre, such as Cookie Clicker. Users who complete this game before the game is removed from the client will also receive an Avatar Decoration that they will be able to use until May.

This is the full game, with al achievements unlocked. Enjoy!
